{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider"]]},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider\/checkInstances(count:for:)"],"anchor":"Instance-Methods","title":"Instance Methods","generated":true}],"metadata":{"title":"TokensProvider Implementations","role":"collectionGroup","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"API Collection"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemepincodeinputcomponenttokensprovider\/tokensprovider-implementations"]}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"references":{"ic_theme_orange.png":{"type":"image","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"title":"Theme Orange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","abstract":[{"text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemepincodeinput